      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "\"I understand your frustration and apologize for the inconvenience caused by the delay of your flight SK402. I've escalated your issue to our team, and they're working to provide a suitable solution. Can you please provide me with your booking reference so I can look into your refund options? I'll also make sure to update you on the status of your flight as soon as possible.\"\n\nThis response aims to de-escalate the customer's anger by:\n\n- Acknowledging their frustration and apologizing\n- Providing a clear next step (escalating the issue to the team)\n- Offering a tangible solution (refund options)\n- Showing a willingness to keep the customer informed\n\nThe tone is empathetic and solution-focused, aiming for a score of around 60-70 on the positivity index.",
