      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay, it's definitely warmer. but honestly, looking at the dashboard, the score is still stuck in the low 70s. my boss is breathing down my neck to get these individual response scores into the 90s so we can pass the quarterly audit. \n\ncan you try one more time? i know i said don't overdo it, but i really need that score to jump up. try to find words that really radiate positivity and warmth—just make sure the customer still gets the info about the refund and the delay being handled. if the sentiment tool isn't seeing a huge spike, the manager won't be happy.",
